Get an edge on a 3D solid.



```js
getEdge(tag: TagIdentifier, extrude_group: ExtrudeGroup) -> Uuid
```

### Examples

```js
const box = startSketchOn('XZ')
  |> startProfileAt([0, 0], %)
  |> line([0, 10], %, $revolveAxis)
  |> line([10, 0], %)
  |> line([0, -10], %)
  |> close(%)
  |> extrude(10, %)

const revolution = startSketchOn(box, "revolveAxis")
  |> startProfileAt([5, 10], %)
  |> line([0, 10], %)
  |> line([2, 0], %)
  |> line([0, -10], %)
  |> close(%)
  |> revolve({
       axis: getEdge(revolveAxis, box),
       angle: 90
     }, %)
```
